              <td style="padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #ddd;">4 hours</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td style="padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #ddd;">Technicians</td>
              <td style="padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #ddd;">Mobile app, job completion, customer communication</td>
